definition: lightning/electricity/electric (bound form)/to get (or give) an electric shock/phone call or telegram etc/to send via telephone or telegram etc

sentences.english: The shock from an electric eel is powerful enough to knock a man out.
sentences.chinese: 電鰻的電擊強大到可以把人擊昏。

sentences.english: Electric eels light up Japanese Christmas tree.
sentences.chinese: 日本用電鰻點亮聖誕樹。

sentences.english: The electric eel stuns its prey with slight electricity.
sentences.chinese: 電鰻會用輕微電流電它的獵物。

sentences.english: Piranha fish live in the lakes, and electric eels.
sentences.chinese: 湖裏有水虎魚，還有電鰻。
